My dot files, apps, and a tiny script to symlink them all.

Be sure to run the following commands after a fresh checkout:

git submodule init
git submodule update

The init command only needs to be executed the first time you do 
a fresh checkout.  The update command needs to be executed the first
checkout or when a change happens within one of the submodules.

To track a newer version of a vim plugin:

cd path/to/plugin
git remote update
git merge origin/master
